Roses – Tang, Ching-Tse
 

 
【呈現與總結討論】
Presentation and 
Concluding Discussion


 
M-1 莊凱婷
〈你說的害怕是什麼？〉
What do you mean about feeling afraid? – Chuan, KT
 
M-2 羅忠韋〈殘室〉
Dilapidated Undercroft – Lo, Chung-Wei
【視狀況延長至13：00】


 
